{"tid":2203953,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[求打救] 被控公安條例 藏伸縮棍","createTime":"2020-09-15T16:44:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-16T03:20:52.000Z","uid":63021,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"8999e0dd2990b6fda8c6fa40cad27399ae1e3a6b","tid":2203953,"uid":63021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T16:44:40.000Z","msg":"- 借朋友 ACC 出 Post - <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有D長篇  <span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">求救</span></span>  <br />\n<br />\n有晚小弟揸揸下車 <br />\n聽到架車有怪聲 就停係高速公路 <br />\n忽然有架警車駛埋黎 查我身份証 <br />\n仲比佢地係<ins>司機位</ins> 搜到支<strong><ins>伸縮棍</ins></strong> <br />\n( 其實係之前買黎傍身用 ) <br />\n<br />\n個黑警就<span class=\"red\">氹</span>我係口供紙認左罪佢 仲話好小事 <br />\n點知 原來係公安條例 33 條 <br />\n<em>最少都要坐 6 個月監</em><br />\n<br />\n我搵左律師幫 <br />\n試下轉簡易程序治罪條例第 17 條 <br />\n<em>有機會唔使入去坐 </em><br />\n<em>但宜家又話可能要坐 2 個月 </em><br />\n<br />\n本來就黎要上庭 又多數要押後 <br />\n係呢個律師度 我已經用左好多錢 <br />\n而佢叫我今次先搵當值律師搞押後 <br />\n收費會平好多 <br />\n<br />\n我同時搵 2 個律師幫 <br />\n會唔會影響法官對我印象唔好？<br />\n<br />\n有無方法可以打得甩？<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">我就黎無曬錢又唔想坐監呀</span></span><br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NJBFbPn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNJBFbPn.jpg&h=d8ca3c55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7inMRPo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7inMRPo.jpg&h=0804c4f0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a51a7b2f1306a6b0f21ef7badec823604c9bc2a6","tid":2203953,"uid":81657,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T16:47:19.000Z","msg":"氹兩氹就搞掂你，樓主呢年幾係咪睏左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68289a5c3a088e19dca4617be12047820ab36dd7","tid":2203953,"uid":9193,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T16:47:32.000Z","msg":"個黑警就氹我係口供紙認左罪佢<br />\n<br />\n你認晒仲可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4eb037257f32a0