mg src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n都係果句，唔好以為一句&ldquo;冇嘢講&rdquo;係免死金牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"869f2a58d4edfe08b7bf3ab140e089231209b36f","tid":2203953,"uid":177168,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T17:05:20.000Z","msg":"搵人食沙律啦"},{"pid":"52a4f291ed851e5ac390557d02d6122bfaa987ca","tid":2203953,"uid":35330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T17:05:23.000Z","msg":"你都認左囉<br />\n不如諗下點求情好過啦<br />\n耶教/叻既朋友/父母"},{"pid":"31d89c7d198d8d4af2e1adec8010b60632404f95","tid":2203953,"uid":121070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"81b6639bb98704b8a668cef5af685bfc3c24ce33","tid":2203953,"uid":189234,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T17:04:18.000Z","msg":"真心唔好喺度問法律意見<br />\n呢度啲人個個無名無姓，你出咗事佢地完全唔需要負責<br />\n<br />\n盡快申請法援，criminal 案件means test算寬鬆<br />\n有乜嘢信律師好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T17:07:00.000Z","msg":"冇撚有錯，睇下幾多賭仔信連登，結果真係得永生，永不翻生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbe29be4ae313f1df13c948b3fe7195c7f0e841b","tid":2203953,"uid":187676,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c64d7757043588ddf17c4f7e1dfbbba5857a2280","tid":2203953,"uid":121070,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T17:04:47.000Z","msg":"伸縮警棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n俾你話&ldquo;無嘢講&rdquo;都唔代表冇事，因為事實真係喺你車搵到<br />\n<br />\n當然你可以話黑警賊贓嫁禍，個官信咪得，如果個官認為有客觀證據證明有動機嘅話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<b