d":128486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T17:40:58.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">律師收咁貴都答唔到你既問題啦</span><br />\n你指意上連登問會比到答案你<br />\n呢幾年你真係瞓左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47b3107497b458d661692fca82b9714a5002e38a","tid":2203953,"uid":54848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"036441b2cca2f292a5a0a110a8cf2191fbe5f7eb","tid":2203953,"uid":63021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T17:40:32.000Z","msg":"我宜家都知認左就無得搞<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">但求希望唔使坐監</span></span><br />\n<br />\n先想問 同時搵 2 個律師幫 <br />\n會唔會影響法官對我印象唔好？ <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T17:41:57.000Z","msg":"唔關事，你而家過堂果個官都未必係審你果個官"},{"pid":"54c14ca6bbd3d6cc3a89eaa5f24e69bde519fa52","tid":2203953,"uid":46187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T17:43:10.000Z","msg":"你應該係上緊裁判法院啦?<br />\ns.33 of Cap.245 有規定只可以判邊啲刑罰, 我唔知你幾歲, 但任何一個判刑選擇我都覺得唔好受嘅<br />\n<br />\n律師可以幫你同doj針下改s.17, 成功與否就睇係邊個prosecutor 啦<br />\n改到s.17使唔使坐好睇你邊個官判, 應該冇律師會實牙實齒咁同你講你唔使坐<br />\n<br />\n轉律師只要唔影響案件進展嘅話法庭唔會介意, 姐係話, 即使你臨上庭先轉律師 你個新嘅律師上到去唔係話未準備好要押後多次嘅話咁其實就冇所謂<br />\n<br />\n如果真係冇錢嘅咪搵民X囉, 你都係裁判法院案件姐? 區域法院先可以及需要搵legal aid"},{"pid":"37e57bcdbde5dbeb1d5676e98f9b4a4fde84679a","tid":2203953,"uid":80503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T17:43:33.000Z","msg":"人地依家問點算唔係上黎被你地屌多轉"},{"pid":"76b26f021c107ea9ab9ef43ba0b6e554069e717d","tid":2203953,"uid":46187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47b3107497b458d661692fca82b9714a5002e38a","tid":2203953,"uid":54848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"036441b2cca2f292a5a0a110a8cf2191fbe5f7eb","tid":2203953,"uid":63021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020